1.  Download iso from Ubuntu Desktop form [Ubuntu ](https://www.ubuntu.com/download)
2.  Download Rufus from [Rufus](https://rufus.ie/)
3.  Run Rufus and make USB  bootable( all the contents on USB will be wiped off, so back up USB first)
4.  Change the boot sequence in Bios and boot from USB
5.  Follow the installtion wizard and finish step by step.
